      <ownedComment xmi:id="d1bf16f3-ef01-4959-9b35-7b8043e3f616" body="The {xor} constraint is applied to a set of associations, specifying that&#xA;over that set, exactly one is manifest for each associated instance. Xor is&#xA;an exclusive or (not inclusive or) constraint." annotatedElement="0e0ac8d5-fb42-47be-b1bd-cd370a6dd2ad">
