      <ownedComment xmi:id="ba575e10-4dd2-4457-a499-0f57abccbe3d" body="A boundary is a class that lies on the periphery of a system, but within it. It interacts with actors outside the system as well as with entity, control, and other boundary classes within the system." annotatedElement="96419f74-37e3-4894-a449-9593f549ffb7">
